\begin_layout Enumerate
A subset from applying relation 
\begin_inset Formula $R$
\end_inset

 on set 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

 is transitive if whenever 
\begin_inset Formula $aRb$
\end_inset

, and 
\begin_inset Formula $bRc$
\end_inset

, then 
\begin_inset Formula $aRc$
\end_inset

.
